<!-- page title -->
<% content_for :title, "New Job Application" %>

  <div class="container-fluid container-lg">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <%= render 'job_posting_header' %>

      <hr />
      <p>
        <%= @job_posting.description %>
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p>Before you begin your application please acknowledge the following:
        <ul>
          <li>
            The Engineering Society is an Equal Opportunity Hiring Organization. No experience is required for our positions.
          </li>
          <li>
            All EngSoc hiring is done according to EngSoc Hiring Policy as seen in Section Gamma of the EngSoc Policy Manual available on our website under "About - Government - Governing Documents"
          </li>
          <li>
            If you have any questions regarding the interview process please feel free to email <a href="mailto:hr@engsoc.queensu.ca">hr@engsoc.queensu.ca.</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Please feel free to contact the Engineering Review Board at <a href="mailto:erb@engsoc.queensu.ca">erb@engsoc.queensu.ca</a> for any concerns regarding the interview process.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        By submitting any application on the Engineering Society Dashboard you hereby declare that the information included is true and complete to the best of my knowledge. In addition, I authorize the hiring committee to verify the information presented here and my eligibility for this position, both at the time of hiring and during my employment. I affirm that any references listed in any of my application have been informed of their usage. I understand that a false statement may disqualify me from employment or cause my dismissal.
      </p>
      <p>
        Interview times will be sent directly to your e-mail. Interviews may start 24 hours after times are posted. Applicants are responsible for being aware of their scheduled interview time. It is the applicant's responsibility to e-mail the listed contact prior to their interview should they need to reschedule.
      </p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="alert alert-info mt">
          <p>
            If you have any accessibility concerns, and require accomodations for any reason, please contact the hiring panel by email ahead of the interview. If you have any specific concerns related to accessibility, please do not hesitate to contact the Director of Human Resources at <a href="mailto:hr@engsoc.queensu.ca">hr@engsoc.queensu.ca.</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <%= render 'job_application_form' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
